## WebSocket Telemetry Pattern
When adding agents, push log events like this:
```python
await telemetry_queue.put({
    "agent": "FUNDAMENTAL",
    "message": "Analyzing Q4 margin compression...",
    "level": "INFO",
    "ts": time.time()
})
```
